        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[疑问]敏感肌就是过敏吗？这是两码事。[摊手]过敏是免疫系统发生的异常反应，常见的过敏原有食物、花粉、尘螨等，表现形式为荨麻疹、水肿等，严重的还可能休克！...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>敏感肌就是过敏吗？<br><br>这是两码事。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[摊手]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_tanshou-fa05d4eacf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>过敏是免疫系统发生的异常反应，常见的过敏原有食物、花粉、尘螨等，表现形式为荨麻疹、水肿等，严重的还可能休克！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>卫子提醒，过敏一定要看医生！而敏感肌是局部皮肤屏障功能被破坏，让皮肤无法抵御外界刺激，从而更容易引发肌肤问题，如泛红、刺痛、干痒等。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（深圳市妇幼保健院）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjopgoe9wfj20u013fgqm.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 03:45:33 GMT</pubDate>
